    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to drive home your dream car? I\u2019m parting with this absolute gem and it is honestly in pristine, showroom condition! It\u2019s been babied since day one\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found. It drives like it just rolled off the lot and looks even better in person. You\u2019ve really got to see this beauty to believe how spotless it is. Don't miss out on this perfect ride!",
