    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system operating in peak synchronization. This example boasts a reinforced subframe and a pristine Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis maintains its factory rigidity with original spec bushings and Bilstein dampers, while the variable M-differential ensures optimal torque distribution. Meticulously maintained with a comprehensive service history including documented valve clearances and rod bearing prophylaxis, this vehicle represents a turn-key performance machine with zero mechanical compromises and flawless original paint.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
