    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior finish is flawless, retaining its original deep luster with no swirl marks, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin feels brand new; the premium leather seats show zero signs of wear, and every electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive, documented service history and incredibly low mileage. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that has been treated with the utmost care. It drives as perfectly as it looks\u2014tight, responsive, and smooth.",
