    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, garage-kept and pampered every single day. You won't find a single scratch or dent anywhere. It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next big adventure. Come take a look, I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love at first sight!",
      "price": 43500.0,
