    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Offered is an impeccable example of the high-revving 5.2L Voodoo V8 powerhouse. This GT350 features the signature flat-plane crankshaft, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,250 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Tremec TR-3160 6-speed manual transmission and a 3.73 Torsen limited-slip rear axle. Chassis dynamics are optimized via the MagneRide active damping system, ensuring exceptional lateral grip and communicative feedback. Meticulously maintained with zero track hours, the undercarriage remains factory-clean and the Brembo braking system retains full bite. A true collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
